dct_title_s: Lʹviv, city plan [cartographic material] = Plan miasta = Stadtplan / [DNVP Kartohrafii︠a︡]. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Also shows wards and generalized land use. Includes inset map: Centre = Centrum = Zentrum 1:12 000. Glossary of abbreviations on recto. On verso: Outskirts Lviv = Okolice Lwowa = Die Umgebung von Lwiw, 1:200 000. Also includes street index, index to points of interest, city chronology, col. ill., and advertisements. Title from panel. "© SSPE 'Kartohrafii︠a︡', 2003, 2005."
